  "text": "Vertebral body heights were used in the assessment of vertebral FR [CITATION_1] and in the assessment of vertebral fractures [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . The results suggested that LAT heights contain the relevant information connected to the vertebral BS. This is probably because they are affected by previous vertebral fractures, the patient's posture, and loads supported by the vertebrae.",
